				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				also according to www.eqtraders.com, you can use any needle-type item HIGHER than the one you need for any of the recipes.<BR>
<BR>
progression is:<BR>
Vah Shir Needle Set<BR>
Acrylia Needle<BR>
Acrylia Needle &amp; Thimble Set.<BR>
<BR>
so something that uses the Vah Shir Needle Set SHOULD be makeable with the Acrylia Needle &amp; Thimble Set, for example.<BR>
<BR>
just passing this along. :)<BR>
<BR>
(none of this is personally verified, and i don't know how the Vah Shir Skinning Knife factors into this, would be lowest rung, but don't know if it's substitute-able)
