				O.K. I decided to raise my skill by making more Black Chitin Belts, even though I can't really create one with them since they are LORE and I wear one...  Anyway, you don't need to hand in a rough belt strap and your knife to get the old needle set.  These belts can be made using the new Acrylia Needle.  Use the belt strap you would have turned in (to make a belt) instead of getting a needle set you no longer need.
