				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Return the rough belt strap (no knife) to get the Vah Shir Needle Set.<BR>
<BR>
Then give him a black chitin belt and a bone beaded belt plus the needle set to get an acrylia needle. You do not get the needle set or the belts back, so give them to another character and do the quest over, so that you will be able to keep a set.<BR>
